original_name: Stella en de tocht naar thuis
plot: Stella, a lovely water elf, activates by accident a magical mirror, which was the prison of the evil witch Misera. Misera is set free and captures Luna, the queen. It's up to Stella to save Luna and defeat Misera once and for all.
